  Magnus walked across the Arctic circle. "I have to get back. They can't 
beat my brother alone."
The oracal appeared in a vision."Before you can help them you must complete 
your training here! Find your way back to them. Then you may help them. And 
when Prime is under control....You may return to Cybertron."
